	//!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
	// This sample App is for demonstration purposes only.
	// It is not secure to embed your credentials into source code.
